'''世界魚類數據庫'''（{{lang-en|'''FishBase'''}}）是一個為搜集[[魚類|魚類]]數據而創立的全球物種[[數據庫|數據庫]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=FishBase Concepts, Design and Data Sources|url=http://fishbase.org/manual/english/contents.htm|accessdate=2020-07-06|work=fishbase.org|archive-date=2017-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170721024635/http://www.fishbase.org/manual/English/contents.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是世界上最大也是訪問最頻繁的魚類數據庫<ref name="Pew">{{Cite web|title=Pew Marine Fellows|url=http://www.pewenvironment.org/research-programs/marine-fellow/id/8589941905|accessdate=2020-07-06|author=Rainer Froese, Ph.D.|publisher=Pew Environment Group|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221164050/http://www.pewenvironment.org/research-programs/marine-fellow/id/8589941905|archivedate=2013-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，很多學術文獻都有引用該數據庫的資料<ref>Stergiou KI and Tsikliras AC (2006) [http://ichthyology.bio.auth.gr/files/tsikliras/d/d3.pdf Scientific impact of FishBase: A citation analysis] {{Wayback|url=http://ichthyology.bio.auth.gr/files/tsikliras/d/d3.pdf |date=20111008223552 }} In: Palomares MLD, Stergiou KI and Pauly D (eds.), ''Fishes in Databases and Ecosystems''. ''[[Fisheries_Centre|Fisheries Centre]]'', Research reports '''14'''(4): 2–6.</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Collaborator Profile - Cada, Robbie N.|url=https://www.fishbase.de/Collaborators/CollaboratorSummary.php?ID=7|accessdate=2020-07-06|work=www.fishbase.de|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514164942/https://www.fishbase.de/Collaborators/CollaboratorSummary.php?ID=7}}</ref>。

世界魚類數據庫提供綜合性的魚類數據，包括分類信息、地理分佈、壽命及形態特徵、物種數量等，也會運用[[營養塔|營養塔]]、[[檢索表|檢索表]]和生態地理學模型，並提供其他數據庫如[[仔魚數據庫|仔魚數據庫]]、[[基因銀行|基因銀行]]和[[IUCN紅色名錄|IUCN紅色名錄]]的鏈接<ref>Gert B and Snoeks J (2004) [http://www.vliz.be/imisdocs/publications/76736.pdf#page=48 "FishBase: encyclopaedia and research tool"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vliz.be/imisdocs/publications/76736.pdf#page=48 |date=20210413160505 }} Page 38, VLIZ Special Publication 17, Brugge, Belgium.</ref>。

{{As of|2011|8}}，魚類數據庫有32100個[[物种|種]]及[[亚种|亚种]]的信息，將近300種語言的292500個[[常用名|常用名]]，50500張圖片，46000條[[科學文獻|科學文獻]]參考<ref>According to the [http://www.fishbase.org/search.php FishBase] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fishbase.org/search.php |date=20170823230232 }} web page, accessed 4 September 2011</ref>。月點擊量達3000萬<ref>{{Cite web|title=Web Statistics|url=https://www.fishbase.de/WebUseAll.php|accessdate=2020-07-06|work=www.fishbase.de|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301191051/https://www.fishbase.de/WebUseAll.php}}</ref>。

==歷史==
世界魚類數據庫的歷史可追溯到1970年代，當時魚類學家[[丹尼爾·波利|丹尼爾·波利]]正在研究魚類的增長是否與其魚鰓的形狀有關係。<ref name="Bakun">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=baUySByM5DIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Ecosystem+Approaches+to+Fisheries:+A+Global+Perspective&hl=en&ei=yQwwTunjOY6emQXOn5j_CA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result|publisher=Cambridge University Press|date=2011-03-03|isbn=978-1-139-49376-5|language=en|first=Villy|last=Christensen|first2=Jay|last2=Maclean|title=Ecosystem Approaches to Fisheries: A Global Perspective|pages=11-23|access-date=2020-07-06|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413192056/https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=baUySByM5DIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Ecosystem+Approaches+to+Fisheries:+A+Global+Perspective&hl=en&ei=yQwwTunjOY6emQXOn5j_CA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result}}</ref>他的假設只有在能夠用大量數據測試時才能驗證。<ref name="Palomares and Bailly">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=baUySByM5DIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Ecosystem+Approaches+to+Fisheries:+A+Global+Perspective&hl=en&ei=yQwwTunjOY6emQXOn5j_CA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result|publisher=Cambridge University Press|date=2011-03-03|isbn=978-1-139-49376-5|language=en|first=Villy|last=Christensen|first2=Jay|last2=Maclean|title=Ecosystem Approaches to Fisheries: A Global Perspective|pages=24-46|access-date=2020-07-06|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413192056/https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=baUySByM5DIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Ecosystem+Approaches+to+Fisheries:+A+Global+Perspective&hl=en&ei=yQwwTunjOY6emQXOn5j_CA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result}}</ref>但當時的數據都散佈於海量的文獻之中，要想得到極其困難。波利便想將所有數據集合在一起建立一個數據庫，令科學家可以方便地探求。<ref name="Palomares and Bailly" /><ref name=AFS >[http://www.larvalbase.org/Downloads/ELHSMay2002.pdf LarvalBase: A Global Information System on Fish Larvae] {{Wayback|url=http://www.larvalbase.org/Downloads/ELHSMay2002.pdf |date=20120328031508 }} ''American Fisheries Society'', Early Life History Section Newsletter, May 2002, '''23'''(2): 7–9.</ref>如果數據可以保證準確無誤，那麼其功效將非常之大。<ref name="Palomares and Bailly"/><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=baUySByM5DIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Ecosystem+Approaches+to+Fisheries:+A+Global+Perspective&hl=en&ei=yQwwTunjOY6emQXOn5j_CA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result|publisher=Cambridge University Press|date=2011-03-03|isbn=978-1-139-49376-5|language=en|first=Villy|last=Christensen|first2=Jay|last2=Maclean|title=Ecosystem Approaches to Fisheries: A Global Perspective|pages=47-54|access-date=2020-07-06|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413192056/https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=baUySByM5DIC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Ecosystem+Approaches+to+Fisheries:+A+Global+Perspective&hl=en&ei=yQwwTunjOY6emQXOn5j_CA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result}}</ref>

波利雇傭了[[溫妮·佛羅伊斯|溫妮·佛羅伊斯]]，在1988年將他们想要的數據庫軟件編碼成功。該數據庫最初只收集熱帶魚類數據。隨後擴大到所有的[[有鰭魚|有鰭魚]]，1996年8月登陸[[萬維網|萬維網]]。現在已經是世界上最大的魚類數據庫。<ref name="Palomares and Bailly" />1995年，其第一張[[CD-ROM|CD-ROM]]以“FishBase 100”為名發佈，隨後每年都有發佈CD。該軟件只能在[[Microsoft_Windows|微軟視窗]]的[[Microsoft_Access|Microsoft Access]]上運行。

魚類數據庫只收集成年魚類信息，並不包括幼年及將近成年的魚類。1999年[[仔魚數據庫|仔魚數據庫]]成立, 其搜集範圍包括[[魚類浮游生物|魚類浮游生物]]、魚卵和幼魚，彌補了世界魚類數據庫的不足。受魚類數據庫激勵，其他的非魚類數據庫也開始成立，包括2006年成立的[[SeaLifeBase|SeaLifeBase]]。<ref name="Palomares and Bailly" />

==當前的組織==
隨著知名度不斷提高，世界魚類數據庫吸引了超過兩千名貢獻者和合作者。2000年開始世界魚類數據庫開始由九個國際機構組成的聯合會來監管。[[基尔亥姆霍兹海洋研究中心|基尔亥姆霍兹海洋研究中心]]則成為其間的協調者。<ref>{{Cite web|title=FishBase : A Global Information System on Fishes|url=https://www.fishbase.de/home.htm|accessdate=2020-07-06|work=www.fishbase.de|archive-date=2022-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423194307/https://www.fishbase.de/home.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=FB3/EV: Ecology, Population Dynamics, and Fisheries|url=http://www.ifm-geomar.de/index.php?id=5118|accessdate=2020-07-06|publisher=IFM-GEOMAR:|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324151446/http://www.ifm-geomar.de/index.php?id=5118|archivedate=2012-03-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

